title: Lunchbox & Amy Review Bobby's GMA Appearance + Garth Brooks Stops By For World Premiere Of His New Song + Dan+Shay In Studio
itunes:title: Lunchbox & Amy Review Bobby's GMA Appearance + Garth Brooks Stops By For World Premiere Of His New Song + Dan+Shay In Studio
description:
Bobby was on Good Morning America yesterday, so Lunchbox and Amy share their thoughts on his interview with Michael Strahan. Garth Brooks stops by to talk about his new single "All Day Long." Also, Dan+Shay stop by to talk about their new album that drops Friday!
